{
  "texts": [
    "The figure shows that keywords with more frequency have larger circles, while keywords with less frequency have smaller circles and are not displayed.",
    "From the cluster graph, it can be seen that \"action recognition\", \"feature extraction\", and \"temporal action localization\" are prominent.",
    "This indicates that TAD is always active in these research fields.",
    "In the figure, \"location awareness\" and \"proposal network\" are darker keywords, indicating that they appeared later; researchers need to pay more attention to these.",
    "In addition, with the development of TAD, tasks such as action prediction and sound localization have been further developed."
  ]
}